Package: metafolio
Type: Package
Title: An R package to simulate metapopulations for ecological portfolio
    optimization
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2014-07-08
Authors@R: c(person(c("Sean", "C."), "Anderson", email =
    "sean@seananderson.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: The metafolio R package is a tool to simulate metapopulations and
    apply financial portfolio optimization concepts to those metapopulations.
    The package accompanies the paper 'Portfolio conservation of
    metapopulations under climate change'. See citation("metafolio").
License: GPL (>=2)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Roxygen: list(wrap = TRUE)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.2),
    RcppArmadillo (>= 0.4.300.8.0),
    plyr,
    colorspace,
    MASS
Suggests:
    knitr,
    devtools,
    TeachingDemos,
    RColorBrewer,
    reshape2
